<p><br></p><hr><h3 id="heading_themen">Themenübersicht</h3><div class="panel panel-danger">
<div class="panel-body">
<b>Hinweis:</b>&nbsp;Die FAQ basieren auf der&nbsp;<a target='_self' class='' data-gentics-aloha-repository='com.gentics.aloha.GCN.Page' data-gentics-aloha-object-id='10007.331665' href="/service/haertefall-fonds-foerderrichtlinie-phase2.html">BMF Richtlinie</a>&nbsp;vom 17.11.2020.&nbsp;
</div>
</div>
<p><a target='_self' class='' data-gentics-aloha-repository='com.gentics.aloha.GCN.Page' data-gentics-aloha-object-id='10007.331665' href="/service/haertefall-fonds-foerderrichtlinie-phase2.html"></a><br></p><div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
<p><a  class='' data-gentics-gcn-url='#' href="#heading_Uebersicht">Übersicht </a></p><p><a  class='' data-gentics-gcn-url='#' href="#heading_Foerderberechtigte">Förderberechtigte</a></p><p><a  class='' data-gentics-gcn-url='#' href="#heading_Foerderkriterien">Förderkriterien</a><br></p><p><a  class='' data-gentics-gcn-url='#' href="#heading_Abgrenzung_zu_anderen_Foerderungen">Abgrenzung zu anderen Förderungen</a><br></p>
