                    </svg>
                </a>
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https://www.wko.at/service/haertefall-fonds-phase-2.html?faq=wkomfaqcontent31" target="_blank" title="Auf Facebook teilen">
